==词源==
“阿丽安萝德”（Arianrhod，来自威尔士语''arian''，“银”和''rhod''，“轮”）这个名字也许与[[原始凯尔特语|原始凯尔特语]]的“*Arganto-rotā”（字母或字词前的星号[*]代表该音位或该语汇单位尚未证实，而仅为基于假定或推测的重建）一词同源，意为“银轮”。
<ref>[http://www.wales.ac.uk/documents/external/cawcs/PCl-MoE.pdf Proto-Celtic—English lexicon] {{Wayback|url=http://www.wales.ac.uk/documents/external/cawcs/PCl-MoE.pdf |date=20060114133008 }} and [http://www.wales.ac.uk/documents/external/cawcs/MoE-PCl.pdf English—Proto-Celtic lexicon] {{Wayback|url=http://www.wales.ac.uk/documents/external/cawcs/MoE-PCl.pdf |date=20110514141136 }}. University of Wales Centre for Advanced Welsh and Celtic Studies. (See also [http://www.wales.ac.uk/newpages/EXTERNAL/E4504.asp this page] {{Wayback|url=http://www.wales.ac.uk/newpages/EXTERNAL/E4504.asp |date=20070310203645 }} for background and disclaimers.) Cf. also the [http://www.indo-european.nl/cgi-bin/query.cgi?root=leiden&basename=%5Cdata%5Cie%5Cceltic University of Leiden database] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060211181501/http://www.indo-european.nl/cgi-bin/query.cgi?root=leiden&basename=%5Cdata%5Cie%5Cceltic |date=2006-02-11 }}.<br>[http://www.wales.ac.uk/documents/external/cawcs/PCl-MoE.pdf ''原始凯尔特语-英语语汇''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.wales.ac.uk/documents/external/cawcs/PCl-MoE.pdf |date=20060114133008 }}和[http://www.wales.ac.uk/documents/external/cawcs/MoE-PCl.pdf ''英语-原始凯尔特语语汇''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.wales.ac.uk/documents/external/cawcs/MoE-PCl.pdf |date=20110514141136 }}. [[威尔士大学|威尔士大学]]高等威尔士语与凯尔特语研究中心. (另见[http://www.wales.ac.uk/newpages/EXTERNAL/E4504.asp ''此页''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.wales.ac.uk/newpages/EXTERNAL/E4504.asp |date=20070310203645 }}以了解背景和免责声明.) 比较: 另见[http://www.indo-european.nl/cgi-bin/query.cgi?root=leiden&basename=%5Cdata%5Cie%5Cceltic ''莱顿大学数据库''] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060211181501/http://www.indo-european.nl/cgi-bin/query.cgi?root=leiden&basename=%5Cdata%5Cie%5Cceltic |date=2006-02-11 }}.</ref>

这个名字最早的形式也许是'''阿兰萝特'''（Aranrot）。如果是这样的话，这个名字的第一部分也许便与“Aran”一词有关。<ref name="Bromwich"/>

